01:27:02.603 --> 01:27:06.170
(INTENSE, DETERMINED
ORCHESTRAL MUSIC)

01:27:06.203 --> 01:27:09.304
POOLE: Officer Gaines was linked
to the Wallace murder

01:27:09.337 --> 01:27:10.735
