01:27:12.370 --> 01:27:16.237
Officer Perez and Officer Mack
were linked to Death Row.

01:27:16.269 --> 01:27:19.503
Once again,
I was told not to look.

01:27:21.437 --> 01:27:23.370
But I had an ace up my sleeve.

01:27:24.369 --> 01:27:27.703
The Gaines family was suing Lyga
and the department.

01:27:27.735 --> 01:27:30.102
And I was the chief witness

01:27:30.135 --> 01:27:32.069
for the defence
of Detective Lyga.

01:27:32.102 --> 01:27:35.036
POOLE: Gaines was a member
of the Rampart Division.

01:27:35.070 --> 01:27:38.337
He was also an associate

01:27:38.369 --> 01:27:41.703
of incarcerated officers
David Mack and Rafa Perez.

01:27:41.735 --> 01:27:44.204
It's my belief
that these officers

01:27:44.236 --> 01:27:46.836
are responsible for
the planning, cover-up

01:27:46.870 --> 01:27:50.337
and the execution
of Christopher Wallace.

01:27:51.768 --> 01:27:54.203
That's some very
explosive stuff, Detective.

