of the public record.

01:28:30.603 --> 01:28:34.236
(DARK, BROODING MUSIC)

01:28:48.735 --> 01:28:50.937
POOLE: But they never let it
go to trial.

01:28:50.969 --> 01:28:55.204
You cut a deal?!
My own team cuts a deal?!

01:28:55.237 --> 01:28:56.770
You're poppin'!

01:28:56.802 --> 01:28:59.403
