all this.

01:32:56.569 --> 01:33:00.937
You have nothing
to feel sorry about.

01:33:00.969 --> 01:33:05.569
Because of you, I came this far.

01:33:09.103 --> 01:33:12.937
(SIREN WAILS IN DISTANCE)

01:33:15.003 --> 01:33:17.502
- Hands behind your head!
- You wonder why we push back.

01:33:17.536 --> 01:33:18.937
That's what you call a guy

01:33:18.969 --> 01:33:20.869
who's in the wrong place
at the wrong time.

01:33:20.903 --> 01:33:22.603
MAN: Our life
is meaningless to you

01:33:22.635 --> 01:33:24.636
because you have the right
to kill us

01:33:24.668 --> 01:33:26.669
based on your theory,
your perception!

01:33:26.702 --> 01:33:28.936
