a young black male.

01:33:28.970 --> 01:33:30.736
OFFICER: Present your wrists.

01:33:30.769 --> 01:33:32.269
(GRUNTS)

01:33:32.302 --> 01:33:35.303
OFFICER 2: Don't resist.
You hear that, motherfucker?

01:33:35.335 --> 01:33:37.003
You hear that?

01:33:38.636 --> 01:33:41.103
POOLE: The sound of sirens
used to mean

01:33:41.135 --> 01:33:44.536
my brother officers were
on their way to assist me.

01:33:44.568 --> 01:33:48.969
Might have been the sweetest
sound I ever heard in my life.

01:33:52.869 --> 01:33:57.136
I was two weeks from my pension
when I resigned.

01:33:59.401 --> 01:34:01.335
I lost my family

01:34:01.368 --> 01:34:07.436
for a case
that I was unable to close.

01:34:09.535 --> 01:34:14.435
And it's just not supposed
to happen like that.

